name: Travelauto
overview:
Travelauto offers reviews and information related to car rental, limousine services and cab services across the globe. The company has its start-up offices in USA, UK and its development center in India.

Apart from providing the car rental reservations, Travelauto also allows users to post their opinions and share it in social media platforms on the services experienced. They also offer users the facility to directly get in touch with their service provider and vice-versa. Renters can post their own notes, plan their travel by comparing the prices and reading the real users car rental reviews to choose the right service provider. Travelauto caters its services to worldwide audience, by engaging car hire companies, and limousine companies from different countries namely USA, UK, Canada, Crotia, UAE, Oman, Saudi Arabia, Ireland, France, Thailand, India and many more.
